<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1059416-is-there-any-romance-in-the-book">Is there any romance in the book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1059416'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F616678.The_Diamond_Throne">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1059416-is-there-any-romance-in-the-book">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1059416-is-there-any-romance-in-the-book">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
